cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about unsupervised domain adaptation for image classification tasks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper proposes a new method that involves deep neural networks and adversarial training, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of the proposed method is done on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
